#: mb/cli/parsing/data.py:148
msgid "Remove duplicate images"
msgstr ""

#: mb/cli/parsing/data.py:150
msgid ""
"Remove duplicate images within and across class directories. Uses perceptual hashing to identify duplicates and moves"
" them to a review directory."
msgstr ""

#: mb/cli/parsing/data.py:159
msgid ""
"Root raw data directory containing class subdirectories (default: raw_data). Typical layouts include multiple class "
"folders under this root."
msgstr ""

