msgid "Create train/test dataset splits"
msgstr ""

#: mb/cli/parsing/data.py:211
msgid ""
"Create training and test dataset splits from raw data. Validates images, removes corrupted files, filters by size, "
"and creates balanced train/test splits with hash-based filenames."
msgstr ""

