"data.test_per_class from pipeline YAML)."
msgstr ""

#: mb/cli/parsing/data.py:242
msgid ""
"fixed = test_per_class images per class; dataset-weighted = modulated counts from class size vs total (default: "
"data.test_split_mode in pipeline YAML, else fixed)."
msgstr ""

